OL,3,C'Gross failure' in hospital care may
OL,4,Chave contributed to disabled woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA coroner has ruled that "gross
OL,8,Ffailure" in the hospital care of a
OL,9,Fdisabled woman "possibly contributed
OL,10,Fto her death".
OL,12,FChloe Every had learning difficulties
OL,13,Fand a muscle-wasting condition and was
OL,14,Fadmitted to Queen's Hospital in
OL,15,FRomford in April 2019 where a scan
OL,16,Frevealed possible signs of bowel
OL,17,Fcancer.
