OL,3,C'Gross failure' in hospital care may
OL,4,Chave contributed to disabled woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe 27-year-old patient was prescribed
OL,8,Fmorphine ` despite it posing a risk to
OL,9,Fpeople with her muscle condition ` and
OL,10,Fsuffered a first cardiac arrest on May
OL,11,F8.
OL,13,FShe was later moved into a general
OL,14,Fward where she died on May 14, 2019,
OL,15,Fin a state of "agitation and pain",
OL,16,Fher family told an inquest last week.
OL,26,@wD@OOUwD@bO]
