OL,7,FAn initial review by the Barking,
OL,8,FHavering and Redbridge University
OL,9,FHospitals NHS Trust subsequently
OL,10,Freferred the case to the coroner in
OL,11,F2019, advising that the cause of death
OL,12,Fwas advanced cancer and myotonic
OL,13,Fdystrophy (MD).
