OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FSenior coroner for East London Graeme
OL,8,FIrvine, delivering his conclusion at
OL,9,FEast London Coroner's Court on Monday,
OL,10,Fsaid these failures "possibly
OL,11,Fcontributed to her death".
OL,13,F"Each of these actions taken alone
OL,14,Fwould not necessarily amount to a
OL,15,Fgross failure," Mr Irvine told the
OL,16,Fcourt in Walthamstow.
OL,18,F"But taken together, the failures in
OL,19,Fcare do amount to gross failure.
OL,26,@rD@UOUsD@YO]uD@AOUwD@OO]zD@AOU
