OL,4,Chave contributed to disabled woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA post-mortem examination of Ms
OL,8,FEvery's body was not held.
OL,10,FMs Every's aunt, Lisa Every, had
OL,11,Fpreviously told the inquest her niece
OL,12,Fwas also given an enema while she was
OL,13,F"still sleeping" on the same day she
OL,14,Fsuffered her first cardiac arrest.
OL,16,FNurse Asia Bawah, who carried out the
OL,17,Fprocedure, had told the court that she
OL,18,Ffelt Ms Every had "consented non-
OL,19,Fverbally".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@PO]zD@SOU{D@IO]
