OL,3,C'Gross failure' in hospital care may
OL,4,Chave contributed to disabled woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FBut Mr Irvine said on Monday the
OL,8,Fevidence showed hospital staff
OL,9,F"haven't got a clue at how appropriate
OL,10,Fconsent procedures should be
OL,11,Fundertaken".
OL,13,FThe coroner also criticised the lack
OL,14,Fof "clear and contemporary records" of
OL,15,FMs Every's care by the Trust's doctors
OL,16,Fand nurses, which meant he was unable
OL,17,Fto apply the legal test for neglect
OL,18,Fand determine whether or not there was
OL,19,Fa "clear causation" between the
OL,20,Fidentified failures and Ms Every's
OL,21,Fdeath.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@KO]vD@DOUvD@cO]{D@COU{D@SO]
