OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Had the doctors of the Trust done
OL,8,Fwhat they were supposed to do under
OL,9,Fthe GMC guidance, I would have been in
OL,10,Fa far better position to determine
OL,11,Fwhether the prescription of morphine
OL,12,Fwas justified," Mr Irvine told the
OL,13,Fcourt.
