OL,4,Chave contributed to disabled woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"If I had not persisted in forcing
OL,8,Fthrough an independent Level 3
OL,9,Finvestigation, the role of the cardiac
OL,10,Farrest in causing her death would
OL,11,Fnever have come out and this inquest
OL,12,Fwould never have been heard."
OL,14,FMs Every's aunt Lisa said: "So many
OL,15,Faspects of Chloe's care heard this
OL,16,Fweek raise serious patient safety
OL,17,Fissues, including failures regarding
OL,18,Fconsent and best interest processes,
OL,19,Fvital where patients have learning
OL,20,Fdisabilities.
