OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Because the Trust failed to properly
OL,8,Finvestigate Chloe's death, it has
OL,9,Ftaken more than four years for the
OL,10,Fcoroner to hear her case.
OL,12,F"It is shocking. Families should not
OL,13,Fhave to force hospitals to properly
OL,14,Finvestigate their errors."
OL,16,FThe BHR University Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,17,Fwill have 56 working days to respond
OL,18,Fto the issues raised in the coroner's
OL,19,Freport.
